# Archived Strategies

This folder contains strategies that have been retired from active use.

## Archive Policy
- Strategies with win rate <45% over 30 days
- Strategies with negative P&L over 60 days
- Strategies replaced by better versions

## Archive Contents
- Original code
- Date archived
- Reason for archiving
- Replacement strategy (if applicable)
- Performance metrics before archive

## Format
Each archived strategy should be saved as:
`archived/strategies/[strategy_name]_v[X.X.X]_archived_[YYYY-MM-DD].py`

